        "subtype": "favored_weapon",
        "text": "*Black Butterfly*, *Brixori*, *Chohar*, *Cosmic Caravan*, *Desna*, *Ma'at*, *Ma\u2019at*, *The Endless Road*, *The Path of the Heavens*",
